45", "image_type": "APP_IMG_IMMERSIVE_LAYER_OBJECT_LEFT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031569_403528738663078_1871676993049865817_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=0uR8rXVWVxkQ7kNvgF5xqyC&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAdK_QbPjuVUvyo-j6wWwUDtz8KrIkEzVMdcGQ6zb1e1w&oe=67371E1E"}]}, "id": "1571573380419322", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "vlcsnap-2024-10-30-13h19m30s202.png", "id": "1301425354549529", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031562_1301425357882862_5517874662819425642_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=X2IKJXTS7SMQ7kNvgE1tb_9&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBKG326C9h2IBWGZiNxXqwxoUvfCroFYK3IFMayzoiWFA&oe=67372B96"}, {"file_name": "vlcsnap-2024-10-30-13h17m24s518.png", "id": "443816104980756", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031373_443816108314089_2920347468317779454_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=kP-td2UlM1MQ7kNvgH6gNIN&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBSpaG6dC8PkHtAPqWpqogwP7N3OmNtq3tbeLcw7IWqsA&oe=673741DA"}, {"file_name": "vlcsnap-2024-10-30-13h20m12s990.png", "id": "1871930603340142", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75262741_1871930606673475_5461235014200294451_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=hnblWbKJjzMQ7kNvgHdUyZK&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDG49Bc_C3QPjrRxEQyULic2FlME2JVlG5JpioUMI4hjg&oe=6737208A"}, {"file_name": "SR_Screenshot_Spiral.png", "id": "667278748607906", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035453_667278751941239_1318060918689432329_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=BlvAICTLQa0Q7kNvgFoSk1q&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBZE-mQmMzSwMEFulgC34TjRANn7-wmZvbXoZVmgu0akw&oe=67372EE8"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_Groove 2560x1440.png", "id": "1321563738659105", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984454_1321563741992438_2719092620761637834_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=zAaOtyBb4DgQ7kNvgGO8GPH&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYApVrGxAlGg8UUaUR7WgqqkbSZjREoTnN16ETpmv2RRqA&oe=67372386"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "Rebrand Quest Landscape (2560x1440).png", "id": "3512198742405543", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39036626_3512198745738876_1477240135308781037_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=tFf0ksizPaYQ7kNvgEuS6O2&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCrjiupJlKfkYsnuYeEdIvwrZkMuGEWpSygSE8LfSrKDw&oe=67371AF1"}, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["music", "rhythm", "beat", "fitness", "mixed"], "long_description": "\ud83c\udf83 Spooky Update is back - find a brand new FREE song in \"Specials\" music pack!\n\nLet the music move you in a unique combination of freestyle dancing & fitness workout that\u2019ll make you to burn calories while having tons of fun, in full VR or Mixed Reality!\n-------------------------------------------------\n\"Accessible, fun, and an absolute must-have for anyone with a VR headset.\"\n9.5/10 - GamingTrend\n\n\u201cAn amazing physical experience that involves the entire body.\u201d\n8.8/10 - VR Fitness Insider\n\n\u201cBrilliant gameplay and exceptional soundtrack.\u201d\n9/10 - Push Square\n\n\u2022 Play, dance & exercise to 75 included tracks\n\u2022 Have fun in 10 player cross-platform multiplayer\n\u2022 Customize your experience with a range of features, including custom song support and Mixed Reality mode.\n\u2022 Play your way with a tremendous variety of gameplay modifiers & styles, such as Spin & Spiral modes\n\u2022 Discover 13 optional DLCs adding 6 visually stunning experiences, 2 extra stages & 67 songs from artists such as Gorillaz, Muse, Bruno Mars, Lindsey Stirling, Caravan Palace & more!", "short_description": "\ud83c\udf83 Spooky Update is back - find a brand new FREE song in \"Specials\" music pack!\n\nLet the music move you in Synth Riders, a dance-action rhythm game packed with 75 included & 67 DLC songs that will make you party all night! Customize your experience with a range of features, including custom song support, multiplayer and Mixed Reality mode.\n\n\"Accessible, fun, and an absolute must-have for anyone with a VR headset.\" 9.5/10 - GamingTrend"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "1091954215968715", "locale": "fr_FR", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["Musique", "Rythme", "Danse", "Fitness", "Beat"], "long_description": "Laissez-vous emporter par la musique dans Synth Riders, un jeu d'action, de danse et de rythme \u00e0 la communaut\u00e9 grandissante, et avec la possibilit\u00e9 d'inclure ses propres chansons !\n\n\u2022 Dansez sur le rythme de 73 chansons aux genres vari\u00e9s\n\u2022 Profitez d'une prise en charge officielle des chansons personnalis\u00e9es\n\u2022 D\u00e9couvrez des DLC vari\u00e9s (Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Muse, The Offspring, Caravan Palace, et bien d'autres)\n\u2022 Faites des sessions \u00e0 10 gr\u00e2ce au multijoueur multiplateforme\n\u2022 Vivez une exp\u00e9rience unique pour chaque chanson gr\u00e2ce aux modes rotation et spirale\n\u2022 Br\u00fblez des calories avec une montre intelligente de fitness.\n\n\u00ab De tous les jeux auxquels j'ai jou\u00e9, c'est celui qui approche le plus la perfection. \u00bb\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u00ab Une exp\u00e9rience physique absolument incroyable qui fait bouger tout le corps. \u00bb\n- VR Fitness Insider", "short_description": "Laissez-vous emporter par la musique dans Synth Riders, un jeu d'action, de danse et de rythme \u00e0 la communaut\u00e9 grandissante, et avec la possibilit\u00e9 d'inclure ses propres chansons !"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "903747827944624", "locale": "zh_CN", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "\u5e7b\u97f3\u9a91\u58eb(Synth Riders)", "keywords": ["\u97f3\u4e50", "\u8282\u594f", "\u8df3\u821e", "\u5065\u8eab"], "long_description": "\u5728\u300aSynth Riders>\u300b\u8fd9\u6b3e\u8282\u594f\u52a8\u4f5c\u6e38\u620f\u91cc\u968f\u97f3\u4e50\u81ea\u7531\u821e\u52a8\u3002\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u6709\u5b98\u65b9\u5b9a\u5236\u7684\u6b4c\u66f2\u548c\u6d3b\u8dc3\u7684\u591a\u4eba\u6e38\u620f\u793e\u7fa4\uff0c\u4e50\u8da3\u52a0\u500d\uff01\n\n\u2022 73\u9996\u4e0d\u540c\u98ce\u683c\u7684\u6b4c\u66f2\n\u2022 \u7545\u4eab\u5b98\u65b9\u5b9a\u5236\u6b4c\u66f2\u652f\u6301\n\u2022 \u63a2\u7d22\u97f3\u4e50DLC\u2014\u2014\u6765\u81eaThe Offspring\u3001Muse\u548cCaravan Palace\u7b49\u4e50\u961f\u7684\u4f5c\u54c1\n\u2022 \u652f\u630110\u4eba\u8de8\u5e73\u53f0\u6e38\u620f\n\u2022 \u5728\u65cb\u8f6c\u548c\u87ba\u65cb\uff08Spin and Spiral\uff09\u6a21\u5f0f\u4e0b\u73a9\u8f6c\u6bcf\u9996\u4e50\u66f2\n\u2022 \u6234\u4e0a\u667a\u80fd\u5065\u8eab\u624b\u8868\u71c3\u70e7\u5361\u8def\u91cc\n\n\n\u201c\u8fd9\u662f\u6211\u73a9\u8fc7\u7684\u6700\u63a5\u8fd1\u5b8c\u7f8e\u7684\u6e38\u620f\u3002\u201d\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u201c\u8ba9\u4f60\u5168\u8eab\u52a8\u8d77\u6765\u7684\u8d85\u8d5e\u4f53\u9a8c\u3002\u201d\n- VR Fitness Insider", "short_description": "\u5728\u300aSynth Riders>\u300b\u8fd9\u6b3e\u8282\u594f\u52a8\u4f5c\u6e38\u620f\u91cc\u968f\u97f3\u4e50\u81ea\u7531\u821e\u52a8\u3002\u6e38\u620f\u4e2d\u6709\u5b98\u65b9\u5b9a\u5236\u7684\u6b4c\u66f2\u548c\u6d3b\u8dc3\u7684\u591a\u4eba\u6e38\u620f\u793e\u7fa4\uff0c\u4e50\u8da3\u52a0\u500d\uff01"}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Korean (2560x1440).png", "id": "4380771405382668", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75324645_4380771418716000_1466639104384545928_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=m3kGRyKsivMQ7kNvgGuGAH7&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAcoX7Pthce-2spNbPpO6BDQxIy19CBIEOBq