5f0f\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0\u66f2\u304c\u5c0e\u5165\u3055\u308c\u3066\u3044\u3066\u3001\u30de\u30eb\u30c1\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u30e4\u30fc\u306e\u30b3\u30df\u30e5\u30cb\u30c6\u30a3\u3082\u5145\u5b9f\u3057\u3066\u3044\u307e\u3059\uff01\n\n\u2022 \u8272\u3093\u306a\u30b8\u30e3\u30f3\u30eb\u306e73\u66f2\u306b\u5408\u308f\u305b\u3066\u8e0a\u308d\u3046\n\u2022 \u516c\u5f0f\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0\u66f2\u3092\u697d\u3057\u3082\u3046\n\u2022 DLC\u30b3\u30f3\u30c6\u30f3\u30c4\u3001Muse\u3084The Offspring\u3001Caravan Palace\u306e\u697d\u66f2\u306a\u3069\u3001\u4ed6\u306b\u3082\u305f\u304f\u3055\u3093\uff01\n\u2022 \u30af\u30ed\u30b9\u30d7\u30e9\u30c3\u30c8\u30d5\u30a9\u30fc\u30e0\u306e\u30de\u30eb\u30c1\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u306710\u4eba\u306e\u53cb\u9054\u3068\u904a\u307c\u3046\n\u2022 \u5168\u697d\u66f2\u306b\u3066\u3001\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u304c\u5909\u308f\u308b\u30b9\u30d4\u30f3\u30e2\u30fc\u30c9\u30fb\u30b9\u30d1\u30a4\u30e9\u30eb\u30e2\u30fc\u30c9\u304c\u904a\u3079\u307e\u3059\n\u2022 \u30d5\u30a3\u30c3\u30c8\u30cd\u30b9\u30fb\u30b9\u30de\u30fc\u30c8\u30a6\u30a9\u30c3\u30c1\u3067\u30ab\u30ed\u30ea\u30fc\u3092\u6d88\u8cbb\u3057\u3088\u3046\n\n\u201c\u4eca\u307e\u3067\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u3057\u305f\u4e2d\u3067\u3001\u6700\u3082\u5b8c\u74a7\u306b\u8fd1\u3044\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\u201d\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u201c\u5168\u8eab\u3092\u4f7f\u3063\u305f\u9a5a\u304d\u306e\u4f53\u9a13\u201d\n- VR Fitness Insider", "short_description": "\u30b7\u30f3\u30bb\u30e9\u30a4\u30c0\u30fc\u30ba(Synth Riders)\u306f\u3001\u97f3\u697d\u3067\u3042\u306a\u305f\u81ea\u8eab\u3092\u52d5\u304b\u3059\u30c0\u30f3\u30b9\uff06\u30ea\u30ba\u30e0\u30a2\u30af\u30b7\u30e7\u30f3\u30b2\u30fc\u30e0\uff01\u516c\u5f0f\u30ab\u30b9\u30bf\u30e0\u66f2\u304c\u5c0e\u5165\u3055\u308c\u3066\u3044\u3066\u3001\u30de\u30eb\u30c1\u30d7\u30ec\u30a4\u30e4\u30fc\u306e\u30b3\u30df\u30e5\u30cb\u30c6\u30a3\u3082\u5145\u5b9f\u3057\u3066\u3044\u307e\u3059\uff01"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "560372979737410", "locale": "de_DE", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["Musik", "Rhythmus", "Beat", "Tanzen", "Fitness"], "long_description": "Genie\u00dfe die anregende Musik in Synth Riders, einem Action-Tanz-Rhythmus-Spiel mit offizieller Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr eigene Songs und einer st\u00e4ndig wachsenden Multiplayer-Community!\n\n\u2022 Tanze zu 73 Songs aus verschiedenen Genres\n\u2022 Viel Vergn\u00fcgen mit der Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr eigene Songs\n\u2022 Entdecke DLC-Songs von K\u00fcnstlern wie Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Muse, The Offspring, Caravan Palace und mehr\n\u2022 Triff bis zu 10 Freunde im plattform\u00fcbergreifenden Multiplayer\n\u2022 Erlebe in jedem Song die bahnbrechenden Modi \u201eSpin\u201c und \u201eSpiral\u201c\n\u2022 Verbrenne mit einer Fitness-Smartwatch \u00fcbersch\u00fcssige Kalorien.\n\n\u201eDas so ziemlich perfekteste Videospiel, das ich je gespielt habe.\u201c\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u201eEine aufregende Erfahrung f\u00fcr den ganzen K\u00f6rper.\u201c\n- VR Fitness Insider", "short_description": "Genie\u00dfe die anregende Musik in Synth Riders, einem Action-Tanz-Rhythmus-Spiel mit offizieller Unterst\u00fctzung f\u00fcr eigene Songs und einer st\u00e4ndig wachsenden Multiplayer-Community!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "493382173702829", "locale": "es_LA", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Synth Riders", "keywords": ["M\u00fasica", "Ritmo", "Futurista", "Ejercicio", "Beat"], "long_description": "\u00a1Deja que la m\u00fasica te gu\u00ede en Synth Riders, un juego de acci\u00f3n y baile r\u00edtmico con soporte oficial para canciones personalizadas y una comunidad en l\u00ednea cada vez m\u00e1s grande!\n\n\u2022 Baila al ritmo de 73 canciones de diversos g\u00e9neros.\n\u2022 Disfruta del soporte oficial para canciones personalizadas.\n\u2022 Descubre DLCs de Gorillaz, Bruno Mars, Muse, The Offspring, Caravan Palace y muchas bandas m\u00e1s.\n\u2022 Juega con 10 amigos gracias al modo multijugador interplataforma.\n\u2022 Sorpr\u00e9ndete con los modos Giro y Espiral de cada canci\u00f3n: cambiar\u00e1n la manera en la que juegas.\n\u2022 Quema calor\u00edas con un reloj inteligente con puls\u00f3metro.\n\n\u00abLo m\u00e1s cercano que he visto a un videojuego perfecto\u00bb.\n10/10 - Pure PlayStation\n\n\u00abUna experiencia f\u00edsica impresionante que involucra todo el cuerpo\u00bb.\n- VR Fitness Insider", "short_description": "\u00a1Deja que la m\u00fasica te gu\u00ede en Synth Riders, un juego de acci\u00f3n y baile r\u00edtmico con soporte oficial para canciones personalizadas y una comunidad en l\u00ednea cada vez m\u00e1s grande!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://synthridersvr.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Kluge Interactive", "support_website_url": "https://synthridersvr.com/contact-us/", "website_url": "https://synthridersvr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1672577396871977"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["MUSIC", "ARCADE", "ACTION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_FOR_DOWNLOAD", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "fr", "de", "es", "zh_CN", "ko", "ja"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER", "MULTI_USER"], "id": "8592936987480814"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035311_1270106287508986_7028552400089566297_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x